        A glittering cold black star-shaped pendant on a adamant chain, this necklace grants its wearer the power to manipulate light. While wearing the necklace, you can cast the darkness spell. You are the center from the darkness and it move with you. Once you use the necklace this way, you canâ€™t do so again until the next dawn. One per short rest you can use this item to cast the spell <em>Speak with Plants</em>.
